{"tid":1435096,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"最重要搵到自己適合做咩崗位，做擅長嘅事","createTime":"2019-08-09T03:02:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T03:05:58.000Z","uid":74908,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"4d2a97d82a008507bd9c7158e6982721f9f90a22","tid":1435096,"uid":74908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T03:02:16.000Z","msg":"見身邊有部份人仲未搵到自己社會中嘅定位<br />\n覺得好迷惘，唔知點好<br />\n<br />\n首先要了解係咪一個<span style=\"color: red;\">夢想家</span>，愛發夢為夢想而戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n定係鍾意<span style=\"color: green;\">文學家</span>，靜靜地以畫/ 文字會友<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當然啦，最好就文武雙全<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">夢想家</span>，首先要夠<span style=\"color: red;\">大膽</span>同<span style=\"color: red;\">判斷力</span>當然要<span style=\"color: red;\">身體健康</span>行得走得<br />\n指揮/ 協助其他人完成你嘅夢想<br />\n<br />\n有<span style=\"color: red;\">經驗</span>嘅人，適合做前線指揮<br />\n因為有唔少追夢嘅人第一次出黎，完全唔知要做咩<br />\n可以指引佢地例如搬運，去邊度視察<br />\n適當時間要帶領撤退，安定民心唔好驚慌而亂陣腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果經驗唔多，不妨聽建議主動幫手<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">文學家</span>，要有文學修養<br />\n識得基本<span style=\"color: green;\">畫畫</span>，<span style=\"color: green;\">寫文</span>，<span style=\"color: green;\">整片</span>或者<span style=\"color: green;\">外語</span><br />\n文人就動口不動手，身體唔夠健壯就以文字作武器<br />\n<br />\n假如覺得自己唔夠文學修養，<span style=\"color: green;\">宣傳轉發</span>訊息已經好足夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n每個人都有價值<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好覺得自己太細個/已經太老，應付唔到<br />\n唔好覺得讀書少轉數慢，幫唔到手<br />\n小小嘅幫忙，或者一句&ldquo;加油&rdquo;<br />\n已經係好大嘅幫助！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1149e234e3ed9f59765cdfd536912cda07f2d324","tid":1435096,"uid":74908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T03:05:58.000Z","msg":"各施其長<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}